{"tid":177343,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過同一個你唔係太中意既人拍咗好多年拖？","createTime":"2017-03-28T19:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T07:51:26.000Z","uid":65819,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d94335bb75784ddb23f3dd267efbc529bfea264a","tid":177343,"uid":65819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:16:01.000Z","msg":"拍咗6年，中學初戀<br />\n嗰時煮到埋黎就食咗。<br />\n<br />\n一直發覺自己其實真係唔係好中意佢<br />\n唔會掛住佢，話題不多<br />\n一開始無乜主動揾佢，<br />\n而家有但純粹係因為覺得作為男朋友有責任<br />\n<br />\n佢d朋友以為我係好男人，專一唔偷食<br />\n其實主要係我怕煩，<br />\n偷食好煩，識過第二個女仔好煩<br />\n嗌交唔氹佢好煩etc<br />\n<br />\n安安穩穩咁就6年<br />\n最近呢種唔知仲一唔一齊好既感覺越黎越強烈<br />\n甚至乎有d好似dear jane首只知感覺失了蹤咁樣<br />\n覺得&ldquo;誰若抽身我連送都不送&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢係個好好既女仔，<br />\n正因為咁我更加內疚<br />\n有無巴絲可以分享吓，<br />\n究竟係人人拍拖耐咗都會有呢個階段，<br />\n定係我地定係唔適合大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef9b86717e42adc40210ef9691a5994333f6b04","tid":177343,"uid":84015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:21:46.000Z","msg":"對你咁好 都係因為背住你食過好多仔<br />\n想彌補對你嘅內疚<br />\n覺得你係將來埋我單嗰個<br />\n唔好分手啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 你條女"},{"pid":"6f539034e75b0aad987373c9cf53ee872b21f7ca","tid":177343,"uid":91393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:24:00.000Z","msg":"男人扑左就等啦<br />\n飛撚左佢識過第條啦 無feel一齊把撚咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff209c583ea7091f9005a25b69fe73be3d7d67f","tid":177343,"uid":50254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:24:01.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔係你身邊你會唔會唔習慣 好似少左啲野咁 仲有你地有無分開過？"},{"pid":"612129e7b3bbed0dc5bcd749bf20c2006013f371","tid":177343,"uid":91393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人扑左就得啦<br />\n飛撚左佢識過第條啦 無feel一齊把撚咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"082974cfe73b12a958f62797db5c5f4049ed6944","tid":177343,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:31:16.000Z","msg":"千萬不要在youtube search賤男<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e959214cae96ff150f8575b70f8d440367f213","tid":177343,"uid":65819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢唔係你身邊你會唔會唔習慣 好似少左啲野咁 仲有你地有無分開過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係分開就無試過，<br />\n但比如佢去旅行 (e.g. 2 weeks)<br />\n我其實無乜掛住既感覺，生活依舊，<br />\n係多咗毒撚一個人食飯咁"},{"pid":"8736405fa78ac066cd0cc0e93e85ccf390513224","tid":177343,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:45:22.000Z","msg":"放開個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bbd373e6143a77cd9c3eded34f3128513ce6a3","tid":177343,"uid":34645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:48:04.000Z","msg":"樓主條件如何"},{"pid":"e54b3f4766d7222b8cd94ec640bdb794945c2ff6","tid":177343,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:50:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9775188e87a3837b26ad1ec3a8d76989f9b97f95","tid":177343,"uid":17170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T19:52:38.000Z","msg":"放生啦 唔好再浪費人地青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee21826a8d14e6a049ece42a0d6241d54bf4a1f7","tid":177343,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T20:20:23.000Z","msg":"賤人"},{"pid":"b3e79c5f66b89d3410f826edc04fd181e7f3e4c5","tid":177343,"uid":86051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T20:21:53.000Z","msg":"遇著你呢種好人<br />\n可能仲慘過遇到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8f628b6c2bc97cb7e625238ef3faa6d5519562","tid":177343,"uid":55013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T20:30:59.000Z","msg":"<block